media:group.media:title: Marvel Goes Full CRINGE | Disney is DOOMED
media:group.media:description:
The Wakanda Forever Clips look TERRIBLE. Disney Marvel's M-She-U Phase Bore ends with the Black Panther sequel, that has the supporting cast vs. a heavily retconned Namor who can't even pronounce his own name. After watching the aforementioned 4 clips, the ones Disney Marvel deliberately picked out to sell this movie, cringe is the only word to describe them. The winds of change are starting to blow. Unfortunately, the more things change, the more Disney stays the same. Too much bad content will lead to apathy, the franchise killer.
